+        self,
+        request: Request,
+        num_encoder_tokens: int = 0,
+    ) -> bool:
+        """Structural capacity check: could the full sequence be resident
+        even if every other block in the pool were free?
+
+        False means no amount of waiting or preemption can ever schedule the
+        request; the scheduler must REJECT it instead of deferring it, or it
+        wedges the head of the waiting queue forever (observed as
+        `num_requests_waiting reason=capacity` for a single long fresh prompt
+        when the real KV pool is smaller than max_model_len suggests).
